# Replace the title with the human-readable specification title, without the document ID.
# The `...` entry expands to the numbered content chapters in filename order, which is why
# references.md and glossary.md must be listed explicitly to stay last.
title: Specification Title
arrange:
  - index.md
  - 00-document-control.md
  - ...
  - references.md
  - glossary.md
